<descript>
<abstract>Jamaica, 1992 is a scanned map of Jamaica at a scale of 50,000. The map is comprised with twenty sheets and georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. The original scanned file with additional information is also provided.</abstract>
<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes. This image may be used in a GIS.</purpose>
